ze: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Recommended Activities in Choroni...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;La Sabaneta is a traditional cocoa estate and is the only fully functioning plantation in the Valley of Choron&Atilde;&shy;. Together with a local employee, you can take a walk through the working grounds of the hacienda to see the cocoa trees and imposing shade trees, as well as the irrigation systems dating from colonial times, giving you an understanding of the development of chocolate from the plant to the bar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Pe&Atilde;&plusmn;ero &lt;/em&gt;(fishing boat)&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;trips to unspoilt beaches such as Uricao and Cepe or the historic town of Chuao (15 to 20 minutes from Puerto Colombia)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A visit to the nearby colonial town of Choron&Atilde;&shy;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Canopying - rapel ascent to three tall trees- with Iguanacci&Atilde;&sup3;n in Puerto Colombia (Jos&Atilde;&copy; David Catena, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:historietas97@yahoo.com&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;historietas97@yahoo.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;, 0414-4009075)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Upon previous request of availability and prices, experienced birdwatchers and adventurers can take you for the following activities:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp; Virgilio Espinal, Vivi: 0416-7473833 | 0243-9911106 | &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@cocuy.org.ve&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;info@cocuy.org.ve&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp; Anibal Balza: 0414-4628854 | anibalbalza@gmail.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Specialised guided nature walks to observe the abundance of plant species such as bamboo, palms, fruit trees, bromelia and flowers &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Birdwatching of the prolific variety of species in the &lt;em&gt;Parque Nacional Henri Pittier&lt;/em&gt;, one of the richest areas in the country for this activity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Birdwatching in the famous &lt;em&gt;Estaci&Atilde;&sup3;n Biol&Atilde;&sup3;gica Rancho Grande&lt;/em&gt; (1.5 hours approx from the Hacienda)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Five hour walk to the historic town of Chuao, producer of the famed Chuao Cocoa, to see its famous grounds and drying patio&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Two hour river trek to the &lt;em&gt;Fundaci&Atilde;&sup3;n Cultural Aguafuerte&lt;/em&gt;, a converted 1950&amp;#39;s dam and electric plant&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Longer mountain treks within &lt;em&gt;Parque Nacional Henri Pittier&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt; ,\n				 property_driving_directions =  ,\n				 property_airports =  ,\n				 property_othertransport =  ,\n				 property_policies_disclaimers =  ,\n				 lat = 0 ,\n				 long = 0 ,\n				 metatitle =  ,\n				 metadescription =  ,\n				 stars = 5 ,\n				\n				 ptype_id = 16 \n				WHERE propertys_uid= 5  :IP: 200.82.220.106', '\r\n5');
